{"type":"message","id":"46118172","parentId":"66a668eb","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:13:02.681Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以，已经实测能调通。  \n\n你这边现在其实已经是这个链路了：\n\n- 技能：`baoyu-imagine`\n- provider：`openai` 兼容接口\n- base URL：`http://69.63.219.95:8080/v1`\n- model：`gpt-image-2`\n\n也就是说，**baoyu 技能本身可以调用你这个第三方 API 来生图**，前提是这个第三方接口兼容 OpenAI Images 风格。\n\n你现在已经可用的方式就是这一类：\n\n- 用 `baoyu-imagine`\n- 指定 `--provider openai`\n- 指定 `--model gpt-image-2`\n- 通过 `OPENAI_BASE_URL` + `OPENAI_API_KEY` 走第三方接口\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接帮你做两件事里的一个：\n\n1. **把它固化成默认配置**，以后你一句“生成张图”我就直接走这个 provider  \n2. **给你整理一份最小可复用命令模板**，你自己在别处也能直接调这个接口","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9b8627484819587f9521c8c567e98\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":36683,"output":250,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776924765722,"responseId":"resp_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9b85f5f40819586c474597d7b51aa"}}
