{"type":"message","id":"61312bd7","parentId":"d797694d","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:14:10.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我建议直接做 **第 1 个，固化成默认配置**。以后你发提示词就能直接出图，最省事。  \n\n顺手我也给你一份最小模板，之后你自己调用也方便：\n\n```bash\nbun /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --provider openai \\\n  --model gpt-image-2 \\\n  --prompt \"你的提示词\" \\\n  --ar 3:4 \\\n  --quality 2k \\\n  --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/out.png\n```\n\n你这边其实已经配好了默认链路：\n- `OPENAI_BASE_URL=http://69.63.219.95:8080/v1`\n- `OPENAI_API_KEY=已配置`\n- `OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL=gpt-image-2`\n\n所以现在开始，你直接给我提示词，我就默认按这个来生图。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9b8a71c7481958fe9f041233495cf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37000,"output":223,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37223,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776924835684,"responseId":"resp_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9b8a512688195a619ff6f18f551dc"}}
