{"type":"message","id":"c65e372d","parentId":"ac64f24c","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:47:23.851Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/6fb1a998-1f23-4c9d-9ec5-be7357942246.jpg (image/*)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths - they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1776926840758-6cc69352\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 14:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1776926843797}}
{"type":"message","id":"1dcf4094","parentId":"c65e372d","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:47:35.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看到了，这张图我收到了。  \n你要我怎么处理它？我可以直接帮你：\n\n1. **参考这张重绘**\n2. **换背景**\n3. **局部修改**\n4. **变成海报风 / 插画风 / 写实风**\n5. **反推出一版适合 baoyu 生图的 prompt**\n\n你直接回我一句目标效果就行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9c0828544819598908cb268dfa07e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":49291,"output":92,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776926843852,"responseId":"resp_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9c07fc1908195a41dd018ad5b36f0"}}
