{"type":"message","id":"cc4a9cc2","parentId":"cd782c04","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:36:04.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"常用的 **baoyu 系列技能**，我这边能调的大致有这些，按用途给你归类一下：\n\n**生图 / 视觉创作**\n- `baoyu-imagine`，通用 AI 生图，文生图、参考图重绘、风格迁移\n- `baoyu-cover-image`，文章封面图\n- `baoyu-article-illustrator`，给文章自动配插图\n- `baoyu-infographic`，高密度信息图\n- `baoyu-slide-deck`，生成幻灯片式视觉页\n- `baoyu-xhs-images`，小红书风格组图\n- `baoyu-comic`，知识漫画\n- `baoyu-image-gen`，旧版生图技能，已迁移到 `baoyu-imagine`\n\n**内容处理 / 转换**\n- `baoyu-format-markdown`，整理和美化 Markdown\n- `baoyu-markdown-to-html`，Markdown 转带样式 HTML\n- `baoyu-url-to-markdown`，网页转 Markdown\n- `baoyu-youtube-transcript`，提取 YouTube 字幕/封面\n- `baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown`，X/Twitter 内容转 Markdown\n\n**翻译 / 改写**\n- `baoyu-translate`，翻译文章和文档，支持快翻、普通、精翻\n\n**发布 / 分发**\n- `baoyu-post-to-wechat`，发公众号\n- `baoyu-post-to-weibo`，发微博\n- `baoyu-post-to-x`，发 X/Twitter\n\n**底层能力 / 特殊能力**\n- `baoyu-danger-gemini-web`，走 Gemini Web 的生成能力\n- `baoyu-compress-image`，压缩图片\n- `baoyu-imagine` 也常被当作通用视觉生成底座来用\n\n如果你问的是 **“最常用、最值得记的几个”**，我建议记这 6 个：\n\n- `baoyu-imagine`，生图\n- `baoyu-infographic`，信息图\n- `baoyu-cover-image`，封面图\n- `baoyu-article-illustrator`，文章配图\n- `baoyu-translate`，翻译\n- `baoyu-post-to-wechat`，发布到公众号\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接给你一版 **baoyu 技能速查表**，做成：\n1. **一句话版**\n2. **表格版**\n3. **按你当前最常用工作流整理版**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9cbc8bb808195adbd654084792c29\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":65039,"output":569,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776929724867,"responseId":"resp_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9cbbe5070819588760ff4baae12ff"}}
