{"type":"message","id":"30242221","parentId":"315a4580","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:38:43.319Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1776929919192-cc08e966\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 15:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nA photorealistic full-body studio portrait of a stunning 22-year-old East Asian woman with flawless fair skin, long straight jet-black silky hair flowing down to her waist, delicate facial features, almond-shaped dark brown eyes with subtle eyeliner, natural full lips with soft red lipstick, looking back over her left shoulder directly at the viewer with a calm seductive expression. She is completely nude, wearing only a pair of glossy black patent leather stiletto high heels with iconic bright red soles (Louboutin style), and a thin silver bracelet on her left wrist.\nShe is kneeling and sitting on a modern white sculptural wave-shaped chaise lounge chair, body angled away from camera showing her bare back, slim toned waist, round firm buttocks, natural trimmed pubic hair visible, side profile of perky medium breasts, long elegant legs. Left hand resting on the back of the chair, right hand supporting her weight on the seat. Soft even studio lighting, clean light gray seamless background, white floor, minimalist high-end photography style, sharp focus, intricate skin texture and hair details, 8K photorealistic, cinematic composition, shot on Canon EOS R5."}],"timestamp":1776929923263}}
{"type":"message","id":"8671df22","parentId":"30242221","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:38:59.464Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我不能帮你生成最后这张，因为它明确要求**全裸成人、可见阴毛和乳房侧面**，属于露骨色情内容。  \n\n如果你要，我可以马上帮你改成两种安全版本之一：\n\n1. **高级时尚写真版**\n- 保留“棚拍、回眸、红底高跟鞋、极简背景、电影感”\n- 改成礼服、丝质睡袍、连体时装或高级内搭外披\n- 依然可以很好看\n\n2. **艺术人像版**\n- 保留姿态、光影、构图、氛围\n- 去掉裸露与私密细节\n- 更像杂志封面或品牌大片\n\n如果你现在是要前一条那个 **“除燥本质在治心” 的卡通信息图**，这个我可以直接做。  \n你只要回我一句：\n\n- **做中医信息图**\n- 或者 **改成时尚写真安全版**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9cc88a2a4819590a2a46162576c79\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":66333,"output":227,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66560,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776929923319,"responseId":"resp_06ece2db478aa7ff0169e9cc84cd70819582f37336ede8e010"}}
